snippet.title: Oscars 2025: Barron Trump Singing "Bless The Lord O' My Soul"
snippet.description:
Bless The Lord Oh My Soul

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
Verse 1:
Bless the Lord, O my soul,
O my soul,
Lift His name on high.
Sing His praise evermore,
O my soul,
Let His glory fill the sky.

Verse 2:
The morning breaks, His love is shining,
His mercy rises with the sun.
Through every trial, through every battle,
I will praise until the day is done.

Chorus:
Bless the Lord, O my soul,
O my soul,
Worship His mighty name.
Sing with joy, sing with love,
O my soul,
Forever He’s the same.

Verse 3:
He's full of grace, His love unending,
His arms are open, strong and wide.
No sin too great, no heart too broken,
In His mercy, we abide.

Chorus:
Bless the Lord, O my soul,
O my soul,
Worship His mighty name.
Sing with joy, sing with love,
O my soul,
Forever He’s the same.

Bridge:
And when my breath begins to fade,
When heaven calls me home that day,
Still my heart will rise in song,
Singing praise forever strong.

Final Chorus:
Bless the Lord, O my soul,
O my soul,
Worship His throne above.
Sing with faith, sing with hope,
O my soul,
Resting in His love.

Outro:
Yes, I'll praise You, Lord, always,
Lifting high Your holy ways.
Bless the Lord, O my soul,
Now and all my days.
